'''Aɣersiw''' d, ɣef leḥsab n [[useggi amagnu|useggi amagnu]], [[Udus (tasnagmant)|amuddir]] [[aẓlazzug|ameẓlazzug]], yetečč tinegwa tigemnawin. Neḥeṛṛ tura irem {{cita|aɣersiw}} i timiliyin i xnezen d [[Udus ageticenbit|ageticenbit]], ɣas ma necukk [[brutuzuwar]] am iɣersiwen ayenticenbit. Am akkw imuddiren, yal aɣersiw yesɛa ikniwen wukud yessileɣ tagrawt tamsarit, i nsemmi [[talmest]]. [[Platon]] yefka-d tabadut agi n awal deg ''[[Épinomis]]''<ref>981b</ref> : {{cita|ayen id fkan asmunu d tadukli n taṛwiḥt d tafekka ddaw yiwet talɣa}}.
